hopobject.body: We work together gymgoal android app The magic ingredients of this compound include the emollient glycerin which hydrates the skin – as, indeed, does the urea present in urine. This recalls the observation by a former builder that when old houses built with lime mortar were being demolished, it was customary to pay someone to “dress” the bricks for reuse by chipping the mortar away. “This made their hands very sore, for which they obtained relief by urinating on them.”
